# 🍕 Pizza Sales Dashboard

This project visualizes sales data from a fictional pizza store to uncover key business insights using interactive dashboards.

---

## 📌 Project Summary

- **Data Source:** Sample dataset by Swapnjeet ([Google Drive Link](https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/17U0ah6Q4MJM_wIn_Xl4fHc-1fO6Q4s6z))
- **Tools Used:**
  - **SQL** – Data mining and query-based segmentation
  - **MS Excel** – Preprocessing and cleanup
  - **Power BI** – Interactive dashboard development

---

## 🧠 Key Insights Delivered

- 📅 **Sales Trends** by day, month, and quarter
- 🍕 **Top 5 Best-Selling Pizzas**
- 💸 **Revenue** by pizza size and category
- ⏰ **Peak Order Times**
- 🎛️ **Interactive filters** for size, category, and date range
